snippet.title: Pixamal Zoo Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
You’ve taken a job as the Zookeeper of a rundown zoo that will soon be turned into a carpark. Improve the zoo and fill it with adorable Pixamals to get more fame and visitors. Only you can save the zoo! So, do you want the job?


In Game Music from https://filmmusic.io:

"Fluffing A Duck" by Kevin MacLeod (https://incompetech.com)
